0a%20near%20hysterical%20period%20of%20rhetorical%20scrambling%20by%20Western%20politicians%20about%20%E2%80%9Cself-defence%E2%80%9D%20and%20the%20myriad%20actions%20that%20might%20be%20brought%20under%20the%20umbrella%20of%20this%20term.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%202001%2C%20as%20the%20world%20watched%2C%20the%20laws%20of%20self-defence%20were%20expanded%20to%20include%20the%20non-state%20actor%2C%20Al%20Qaeda%2C%20and%20Afghanistan%2C%20the%20state%20harbouring%20the%20non-state%20actor.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20invasion%20also%20upended%20what%20the%20West%20said%20they%20believed%20were%20universal%20human%20rights%20%E2%80%93%20torture%2C%20extra-territorial%20rendition%20(the%20kidnap%20and%20the%20export%20of%20prisoners%20to%20other%20jurisdictions%20for%20interrogation)%20and%20the%20indefinite%20detention%20of%20prisoners%20without%20trial%20or%20release%20became%20commonplace.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%202003%2C%20the%20US%20and%20the%20UK%20convinced%20everyone%20and%20themselves%20that%20Saddam%20Hussein%20was%20sitting%20on%20a%20pile%20of%20%E2%80%9Cweapons%20of%20mass%20destruction%E2%80%9D.%20An%20invasion%20of%20Iraq%2C%20they%20said%2C%20was%20the%20only%20way%20for%20them%20to%20%E2%80%9Cdefend%E2%80%9D%20themselves.%20Self-defence%20was%20stretched%20once%20more%20(goodbye%2C%20imminence)%20and%20Iraq%20was%20invaded.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20many%20Western%20leaders%20outdid%20themselves%20in%20a%20%E2%80%9Cwhat%20war%20crime%20is%20actually%20just%20self-defence%E2%80%9D%20contest.%20UK%20Labour%20Party%20leader%20Kier%20Starmer%20went%20on%20live%20television%20and%20said%20that%20the%20Israelis%20had%20the%20right%20to%20turn%20off%20water%20and%20power%20to%20civilians%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnd%20when%20asked%20if%20he%20would%20ask%20the%20Israelis%20to%20end%20the%20collective%20punishment%20of%20Gaza%20civilians%20by%20Israel%2C%20British%20PM%20Rishi%20Sunak%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aa.com.tr%2Fen%2Feurope%2Fuk-premier-avoids-urging-israel-to-end-collective-punishment-in-gaza%2F3022718%5C%22%3Eresponded%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20actually%20believe%20that%20we%20should%20support%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20right%20to%20defend%20itself%20and%20to%20go%20after%20Hamas%20and%20recognising%20that%20they%20(Israel)%20face%20a%20vicious%20enemy%20that%20embeds%20itself%20behind%20civilians.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUS%20President%20Joe%20Biden%2C%20whose%20rhetoric%20about%20%E2%80%9Cfreedom%E2%80%9D%20and%20the%20US%E2%80%99s%20role%20in%20the%20world%20has%20sounded%20increasingly%20like%20a%20throwback%20tape%20out%20of%202001%2C%20has%20refused%20to%20hold%20Israel%20accountable%20for%20any%20actions%20that%20human%20rights%20groups%20have%20termed%20war%20crimes%20and%20seems%20to%20have%20no%20ability%20or%20will%20to%20influence%20Israel%20to%20respect%20even%20the%20most%20basic%20humanitarian%20norms%20for%20Palestinian%20civilians.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20while%20the%20rhetoric%20is%20reminiscent%20of%20the%20post-9%2F11%20days%2C%20it%20is%20useful%20to%20remember%20that%20the%20world%20is%20not%20the%20same.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20United%20States%20never%20fully%20recovered%20its%20pre-9%2F11%20position%20or%20credibility%20and%20its%20own%20internal%20systemic%20brutality%20is%20less%20hidden%20than%20it%20used%20to%20be.%20Young%20Americans%2C%20well%20versed%20in%20analysing%20the%20expressions%20of%20this%20systemic%20brutality%20in%20print%2C%20have%20become%20far%20more%20savvy%20than%20previous%20generations%20in%20sifting%20through%20propaganda.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESocial%20media%20nitpicking%20has%20also%20made%20people%20hyper-aware%20of%20the%20tricks%20newspapers%20use%20to%20dehumanise%2C%20like%20using%20passive%20voice%20when%20reporting%20people%20killed%20by%20airstrikes%2C%20or%20routinely%20holding%20only%20one%20side%20accountable%20for%20acts%20of%20violence%20against%20civilians.%20People%20getting%20their%20Palestinian%20history%20from%20TikTok%20may%20not%20quite%20be%20getting%20the%20full%20picture%2C%20they%20are%20still%20getting%20more%20than%20they%20otherwise%20would%20have%20in%20the%20United%20States.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EI%20had%20written%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftattva.substack.com%2Fp%2Fisrael-india-and-the-limits-of-diaspora%5C%22%3Ein%202021%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0about%20social%20media%20changing%20Palestinian%20narratives%20in%20the%20US.%20In%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.gallup.com%2Fpoll%2F472070%2Fdemocrats-sympathies-middle-east-shift-palestinians.aspx%23%3A~%3Atext%3DStory%2520Highlights%26amp%3Btext%3DWASHINGTON%2C%2520D.C.%2C%2C%252049%2525%2520versus%252038%2525.%5C%22%3EGallup%20polling%20conducted%20in%20March%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%2049%25%20of%20democrats%20said%20their%20sympathies%20lay%20with%20the%20Palestinian%20people%20and%20only%2038%25%20said%20their%20sympathies%20lay%20with%20Israel.%20This%20marks%20a%20significant%20shift%20in%20American%20public%20opinion%20which%20had%20hitherto%20uncritically%20supported%20Israel%20across%20party%20lines.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20aftermath%20of%20October%207%2C%20despite%20heavy%20crackdowns%20in%20which%20students%20have%20been%20accused%20of%20anti-Semitism%2C%20doxxed%20and%20have%20lost%20job%20offers%2C%20and%20immigrants%20have%20been%20threatened%20with%20the%20cancellation%20of%20their%20visas%2C%20the%20pushback%20against%20Israeli%20narratives%20in%20the%20West%20has%20been%20strong.%20And%20it%20has%20gone%20beyond%20Palestinian%20or%20Arab%20voices.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Israeli%20Settlers%20Are%20Using%20the%20Ongoing%20Violence%20to%20Ethnically%20Cleanse%20Palestinians%20in%20Jordan%20Valley%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fisraeli-settlers-are-using-the-ongoing-violence-to-ethnically-cleanse-palestinians-in-jordan-valley%5C%22%3EIsraeli%20Settlers%20Are%20Using%20the%20Ongoing%20Violence%20to%20Ethnically%20Cleanse%20Palestinians%20in%20Jordan%20Valley%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EJewish%20anti-Zionist%20groups%20have%20organised%20sit-ins%20in%20the%20Capitol%20demanding%20a%20ceasefire%20and%20a%20series%20of%20pro-Palestinian%20rallies%20in%20New%20York%20and%20other%20American%20cities%20have%20drawn%20unprecedented%20numbers.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAcross%20Europe%2C%20governments%20have%20done%20their%20best%20to%20curb%20expressions%20of%20support%20for%20the%20Palestinian%20people%2C%20and%20yet%2C%20these%20have%20largely%20failed.%20France%20banned%20pro-Palestine%20protests%2C%20and%20yet%20a%20protest%20held%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20ban%20drew%20immense%20crowds.%20Yesterday%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fworld%2F2023%2Foct%2F21%2Fabout-100000-turn-out-in-london-for-pro-palestine-rally%5C%22%3Ethe%20London%20metropolitan%20police%20confirmed%20that%20at%20least%20100%2C000%3C%2Fa%3E%20attended%20a%20protest%20in%20London%20to%20show%20their%20support%20for%20the%20Palestinian%20cause.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnd%20added%20to%20all%20of%20this%20has%20been%20the%20constant%20and%20extremely%20painful%20documentation%20of%20the%20ongoing%20suffering%20of%20the%20people%20of%20Gaza%20by%20journalists%20based%20in%20Gaza%20who%20have%20not%20stopped%20telling%20their%20stories%20despite%20facing%20bombardment%2C%20hunger%2C%20thirst%20and%20homelessness.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20longstanding%20dehumanisation%20of%20the%20Palestinian%20people%20in%20the%20Western%20media%20narrative%2C%20this%20has%20not%20been%20without%20impact.%20In%20%3Ca%20rel%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dataforprogress.org%2Fblog%2F2023%2F10%2F19%2Fvoters-agree-the-us-should-call-for-a-ceasefire-and-de-escalation-of-violence-in-gaza%5C%22%3Ea%20poll%20conducted%20on%20October%2020%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3Ein%20the%20United%20States%2C%2066%25%20of%20voters%20across%20party%20lines%20said%20that%20they%20supported%20the%20US%20calling%20for%20an%20immediate%20ceasefire%20and%20a%20de-escalation%20of%20violence%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnd%20yet%2C%20none%20of%20this%20has%20managed%20to%20call%20a%20halt%20to%20the%20ongoing%20brutality%20faced%20by%20Palestinian%20civilians.%20%3Ca%20rel%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Freliefweb.int%2Freport%2Foccupied-palestinian-territory%2Fgaza-escalation-update-2-19th-october-2023%5C%22%3ETwenty-five%20percent%20of%20all%20civilian%20houses%20in%20Gaza%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0have%20been%20destroyed.%20According%20to%20the%20Palestinian%20Ministry%20of%20Health%2C%204%2C385%20civilians%20have%20been%20killed%2C%20including%201%2C750%20children%20in%20the%20last%20two%20weeks%20alone%20and%20close%20to%20a%20million%20people%20have%20been%20internally%20displaced.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFood%2C%20water%2C%20fuel%20and%20medical%20supplies%20to%20Gaza%20remain%20entirely%20cut%20(with%20the%20exception%20of%2020%20trucks%20of%20humanitarian%20aid%20that%20passed%20through%20the%20Egyptian%20border)%20and%20Israeli%20airstrikes%20have%20severely%20damaged%20cultural%20heritage%20including%20one%20of%20the%20oldest%20churches%20in%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Western%20world%20terms%20this%20%E2%80%9Ca%20humanitarian%20crisis%E2%80%9D%20but%20it%20is%20increasingly%20difficult%20to%20argue%20that%20this%20is%20not%20an%20ongoing%20campaign%20of%20ethnic%20cleansing.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20a%20stark%20reminder%20that%20while%20narratives%20can%20and%20do%20change%20over%20time%2C%20they%20have%20not%20changed%20quickly%20enough%20for%20the%20Palestinian%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fsarayu-pani%5C%22%3ESarayu%20Pani%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20former%20lawyer%20and%20tweets%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsarayupani%5C%22%3E%40sarayupani%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20has%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftattva.subst