20the%20rights%20of%20Palestinians%20who%20are%20citizens%20of%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20Israel%20has%20a%20Law%20of%20Return%20which%20allows%20Jews%20from%20anywhere%20in%20the%20world%20to%20come%20to%20Israel%20and%20get%20automatic%20citizenship%20but%20family%20members%20of%20Palestinians%2C%20who%20were%20born%20in%20Palestine%20but%20left%20at%20the%20time%20of%20the%20nakba%20or%201967%20war%2C%20are%20specifically%20and%20explicitly%20denied%20this%20right.%20Iriqat%20points%20out%20this%20is%20in%20defiance%20of%20UN%20Resolution%20194%2C%20which%20conferred%20on%20all%20Palestinians%20the%20right%20to%20return%20to%20their%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIriqat%20also%20talks%20about%20how%20Hamas%20is%20viewed%20by%20the%20three%20categories%20of%20Palestinians.%20She%20also%20speaks%20about%20how%20popular%20it%20is%20in%20Gaza%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAsked%20if%20a%20free%2C%20fair%20and%20credible%20election%20were%20to%20be%20held%20in%20Gaza%20today%2C%20the%20way%20it%20had%20happened%20in%202006%2C%20would%20Hamas%20win%20a%20victory%2C%20Iriqat%20categorically%20said%20no.%20In%20fact%2C%20she%20clearly%20suggested%20that%20a%20free%20and%20fair%20election%20is%20perhaps%20the%20best%20way%20of%20diminishing%20and%20reducing%20Hamas.%20But%20the%20Israelis%2C%20she%20says%2C%20will%20not%20allow%20a%20free%20and%20fair%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20Iriqat%20says%20she%20agrees%20with%20what%20Gideon%20Levy%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fvideo-gideon-levy-karan-thapar-gaza-israel-palestine%5C%22%3Eearlier%20interview%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%93%20a%20one-state%20solution%20would%20be%20the%20ideal%20answer%20provided%2C%20of%20course%2C%20there%20are%20equal%20rights%20for%20Jews%20and%20Arabs.%20She%20agreed%20that%20a%20two-state%20solution%20is%20no%20longer%20feasible%20or%20practical.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen