ress-2023-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Senate%20Minority%20Leader%20Mitch%20McConnell%2C%20who%20is%2081%20years%20old%2C%20shut%20down%20questions%20about%20his%20health%20on%20Sunday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22sankel%40businessinsider.com%20(Sophia%20Ankel)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmitch-mcconnell-says-in-good-shape-ignores-question-fit-congress-2023-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Dollar%20General%20took%20back%20job%20offers%20from%20applicants%20with%20high%20blood%20pressure%20and%20poor%20eyesight%2C%20a%20federal%20agency%20lawsuit%20claimed%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22dollar%20general%20storefront%20people%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6478ff1830404300183aaa77%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22669%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDollar%20General%20rescinded%20job%20offers%20to%20some%20applicants%20with%20high%20blood%20pressure%20or%20poor%20eyesight%2C%20the%20EEOC%20claims.%3Cp%3EAP%20Photo%2FEric%20Gay%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EDollar%20General%20rescinded%20job%20offers%20to%20applicants%20with%20high%20blood%20pressure%20or%20poor%20eyesight%2C%20an%20EEOC%20lawsuit%20claims.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EApplicants%20to%20its%20warehouse%20in%20Bessemer%2C%20Alabama%20had%20to%20complete%C2%A0%26quot%3Bextensive%26quot%3B%20medical%20exams%2C%20per%20the%20EEOC.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20discount%20retailer%20has%20agreed%20to%20pay%20%241%20million%20to%20settle%20the%20disability-discrimination%20lawsuit.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EDollar%20General%20violated%20disability-discrimination%20laws%20by%20rescinding%20job%20offers%20to%20some%20applicants%20with%20high%20blood%20pressure%20or%20poor%20eyesight%2C%20a%20federal%20agency%20said%20in%20a%20lawsuit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20discount%20retailer%20has%20now%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eeoc.gov%2Fnewsroom%2Fdollar-general-pay-1-million-settle-eeoc-disability-and-gina-lawsuit%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eagreed%20to%20pay%20%241%20million%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20settle%20the%20lawsuit%2C%20first%20filed%20by%20the%20Equal%20Employment%20Opportunity%20Commission%20in%202017.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDollar%20General%20required%20people%20who%20held%20offers%20for%20roles%20as%20general%20warehouse%20workers%20at%20its%20Bessemer%2C%20Alabama%20distribution%20center%20to%20pass%20a%20pre-employment%20medical%20examination%2C%20the%20lawsuit%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20EEOC%20said%20the%20medical%20examinations%20were%20%26quot%3Bextensive%2C%20and%20often%2C%20highly%20invasive%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20included%20taking%20vital%20signs%2C%20a%20drug%20test%2C%20a%20vision%20test%2C%20a%20review%20of%20current%20medications%2C%20%26quot%3Band%20a%20physical%20examination%2C%20including%2C%20in%20some%20instances%2C%20genital%20examination%20of%20job%20applicants.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20retailer%20rescinded%20job%20offers%20for%20some%20qualified%20individuals%20with%20disabilities%2C%20even%20when%20these%20wouldn't%20affect%20their%20ability%20to%20safely%20carry%20out%20the%20job%2C%20the%20EEOC's%20suit%20claimed.%20These%20included%20offer-holders%20whose%20blood%20pressure%20exceeded%20160%2F100%20or%20who%20didn't%20have%20at%20least%2020%2F50%20vision%20in%20both%20eyes%2C%20according%20to%20the%20lawsuit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20examinations%20also%20included%20health%20questionnaires%20during%20which%20offer-holders%20had%20to%20divulge%20their%20family%20members'%20past%20and%20present%20medical%20conditions%2C%20including%20cancer%2C%20diabetes%2C%20and%20heart%20disease%2C%20the%20lawsuit%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDollar%20General%20dismissed%20candidates%20based%20on%20the%20results%20of%20their%20medical%20examinations%2C%20and%20the%20selection%20criteria%20%26quot%3Bwere%20not%20job%20related%20or%20consistent%20with%20business%20necessity%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20EEOC%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20EEOC%20filed%20its%20lawsuit%20in%20the%20US%20District%20Court%20for%20the%20Northern%20District%20of%20Alabama%2C%20alleging%20that%20Dollar%20General's%20hiring%20process%20violated%20the%20Americans%20with%20Disabilities%20Act%20(ADA)%20and%20the%20Genetic%20Information%20Non-Discrimination%20Act%20(GINA).%20The%20company%20stopped%20requiring%20pre-employment%20medical%20exams%20for%20these%20warehouse%20jobs%20after%20the%20lawsuit%20was%20filed%2C%20the%20EEOC%20said%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eeoc.gov%2Fnewsroom%2Fdollar-general-pay-1-million-settle-eeoc-disability-and-gina-lawsuit%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epress%20release%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDollar%20General%20said%20in%20a%20response%20to%20the%20lawsuit%20in%202018%20that%20its%20employment%20decisions%20were%20made%20for%20%26quot%3Blegitimate%2C%20non-discriminatory%20business%20reasons%20and%20not%20for%20any%20unlawful%20or%20improper%20purpose.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAny%20alleged%20discriminatory%20or%20otherwise%20unlawful%20behavior%20imputed%20to%20Dollar%20General%20was%20neither%20intentional%2C%20knowing%2C%20reckless%2C%20nor%20malicious%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20retailer%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDollar%20General%20acknowledged%20that%20offer-holders%20did%20have%20to%20complete%20a%20physical%20assessment%2C%20carried%20out%20by%20a%20third-party%20health%20provider%2C%20before%20they%20could%20be%20formally%20hired.%20However%2C%20it%20denied%20unlawfully%20seeking%20genetic%20information%20by%20asking%20offer-holders%20to%20complete%20a%20family%20medical-history%20questionnaire%2C%20and%20said%20that%20if%20this%20questionnaire%20was%20required%20by%20the%20provider%20then%20it%20was%20done%20without%20the%20knowledge%20of%20Dollar%20General.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20parties'%20settlement%20agreement%20was%20approved%20by%20Judge%20Madeline%20Hughes%20Haikala%20on%20October%2018.%20As%20well%20as%20paying%20%241%20million%20to%20affected%20applicants%20for%20warehouse%20worker%20roles%20at%20the%20Bessemer%20site%2C%20Dollar%20General%20agreed%20to%20review%20and%20revise%20its%20ADA%20and%20GINA%20policies%2C%20train%20all%20hiring%20staff%20on%20this%20annually%2C%20and%20require%20its%20medical%20examiners%20not%20to%20request%20family%20medical%20history%2C%20the%20settlement%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRequiring%20individuals%20during%20the%20hiring%20process%20to%20answer%20invasive%20questions%20about%20medical%20conditions%20of%20their%20grandparents%2C%20parents%20or%20children%20violates%20GINA%2C%26quot%3B%20Bradley%20Anderson%2C%20the%20EEOC's%20district%20director%20in%20Birmingham%2C%20Alabama%2C%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%20%26quot%3BAn%20employer%20is%20prohibited%20from%20soliciting%20this%20information%2C%20regardless%20of%20whether%20the%20information%20is%20used%20to%20deny%20employment.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInsider%20contacted%20Dollar%20General%20for%20comment%2C%20but%20did%20not%20immediately%20receive%20a%20response%2C%20outside%20regular%20US%20business%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdollar-general-took-back-job-offers-blood-pressure-eyesight-discrimination-2023-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698057176000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F653643cf96908fd7cdb4ec25%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdollar-general-took-back-job-offers-blood-pressure-eyesight-discrimination-2023-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Dollar%20General%20has%20agreed%20to%20pay%20%241%20million%20to%20settle%20the%20disability-discrimination%20lawsuit%20filed%20by%20the%20EEOC.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22gdean%40insider.com%20(Grace%20Dean)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.busin