jumps-into-poll-fray-again%2Farticleshow%2F104649482.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Most%20Scams%20Under%20Shivraj%20Govt%20in%20Schemes%20for%20Poor%E2%80%99%3A%20Congress%20Candidate%20and%20Whistleblower%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F23153620%2Fcensored.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EShivraj%20Sarkar%20ka%20matlab%20hi%2050%25%20commission%20hain%3C%2Fem%3E.%E2%80%9D%20(The%20Shivraj%20Singh%20Chouhan%20government%20is%20synonymous%20with%2050%25%20commission).%20Printed%20in%20saffron%20font%2C%20this%20one-line%20indictment%20of%20the%20BJP%20government%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20was%20part%20of%20the%20preface%20to%20a%20document%20released%20by%20its%20rival%20Congress%2C%20listing%20the%20incumbent%E2%80%99s%20alleged%20scams%20in%20its%2018%20years%20in%20power.%20With%20a%20copy%20of%20this%20placard%20in%20hand%2C%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20chief%20minister%20candidate%20Kamal%20Nath%20in%20August%20released%20an%20%3Cem%3EAarop%20Patra%3C%2Fem%3E%20(chargesheet)%20of%20alleged%20corruption%20and%20scams%20under%20the%20Chouhan%20government.%20The%20document%20was%20titled%20%E2%80%9CGhotala%20hi%20Ghotala%E2%80%93Ghotala%20seth%2C%2050%25%20commission%20rate%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20direct%20dig%20at%20Chouhan%2C%20who%20is%20described%20as%20%E2%80%98Lootera%20Mama%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EStanding%20alongside%20Nath%20at%20the%20release%20was%20a%20wavy-haired%20man%20with%20a%20geeky%20appearance%20who%20has%20often%20been%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20the%20fight%20against%20corruption%20in%20the%20state%3A%20Paras%20Saklecha.%20He%20played%20a%20significant%20role%20in%20drafting%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98chargesheet%E2%80%99%20against%20Chouhan%2C%20one%20that%20has%20underlined%20corruption%20as%20a%20major%20point%20of%20attack%20in%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20campaign%20against%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20mathematics%20tutor-cum-politician%2C%20Saklecha%20is%20a%20former%20independent%20MLA.%20He%20joined%20the%20Congress%20in%202018%2C%20months%20before%20the%20state%20voted%20that%20year.%20In%20the%202023%20assembly%20election%2C%20the%20Congress%20has%20fielded%20him%20from%20Ratlam%2C%20a%20constituency%20in%20the%20Malwa%20region.%20Saklecha%2C%20fondly%20referred%20to%20as%20%3Cem%3Edada%3C%2Fem%3E%20(elder%20brother)%20by%20students%2C%20argues%20that%20corruption%20was%20among%20the%20top%20three%20issues%20that%20count%20go%20against%20the%20Chouhan%20government%20in%20the%20November%2017%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20will%20face%20heavy%20losses%20due%20to%20their%20corruption%2C%20which%20has%20increased%20at%20all%20levels.%20There%20is%20corruption%20everywhere%20in%20the%20state%2C%20whether%20you%20have%20to%20get%20any%20enrolment%20done%20or%20want%20an%20Ayushman%20Bharat%20card%20or%20BPL%20coupon%20made.%20The%20administration%20is%20unrestrained%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETalking%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Saklecha%20alleged%20that%20an%20overwhelmingly%20high%20number%20of%20alleged%20corruption%20scams%20in%20MP%20had%20taken%20place%20in%20welfare%20schemes%20for%20the%20poor.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20were%20supposed%20to%20bolster%20the%20financial%20condition%20of%20the%20poor.%20But%20that%20did%20not%20happen.%20Instead%2C%20the%20mafia%20swallowed%20all%20the%20funds%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20Aarop%20Patra%20mentions%20over%20225%20%E2%80%9Cscams%E2%80%9D%20under%20the%20Chouhan%20government%2C%20including%20charges%20of%20direct%20financial%20irregularities%20along%20with%20instances%20of%20misgovernance%20and%20mismanagement.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20top%20of%20the%20list%20is%20the%20alleged%20Poshan%20Ahar%20%E2%80%98scam%E2%80%99%20related%20to%20the%20supplementary%20nutrition%20scheme%20run%20by%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20Women%20and%20Child%20Development%20Department.%20Citing%20a%20report%20by%20the%20Accountant%20General%2C%20the%20Congress%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Fpolitics-and-nation%2Fcongress-cites-audit-to-allege-ration-scam-under-mp-cms-watch-govt-says-ag-report-not-final-conclusion%2Farticleshow%2F94032704.cms%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20vehicles%20mentioned%20as%20trucks%20meant%20to%20distribute%20ration%20under%20the%20scheme%2C%20were%20found%20to%20be%20motorcycles%2C%20autos%20and%20tractors.%20The%20Congress%20also%20alleged%20that%2011%2C000%20metric%20tonnes%20of%20take-home%20ration%20was%20distributed%20to%20beneficiaries%20only%20on%20paper.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAlso%20featured%20in%20the%20Congress%20chargesheet%20is%20the%20alleged%20irregularity%20in%20the%20recruitment%20of%20contractual%20nursing%20staff%20under%20the%20National%20Health%20Mission.%20The%20recruitment%20process%20of%20the%20scheme%20came%20under%20the%20scanner%20earlier%20this%20year%20after%20the%20exam%20paper%20was%20leaked.%20The%20exams%20were%20held%20for%20recruitment%20on%202%2C284%20posts%2C%20for%20which%2045%2C000%20candidates%20were%20to%20appear.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20embers%20of%20the%20infamous%20%E2%80%9CVyapam%20Scam%E2%80%9D%20in%20Chouhan%E2%80%99s%20previous%20terms%20have%20gradually%20died%20out%2C%20fresh%20allegations%20in%20the%20recruitment%20process%20of%20Patwaris%20(revenue%20department%20staffers)%20have%20rocked%20the%20government.%20The%20matter%2C%20labelled%20the%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fvyapam-fresh-alelgations-recruitment-scam-madhya-pradesh%5C%22%3EPatwari%20Recruitment%20Scam%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D%20by%20the%20Congress%2C%20came%20to%20light%20after%20it%20was%20found%20that%20seven%20out%20of%20the%20top%2010%20candidates%20who%20had%20taken%20the%20online%20examination%20for%20the%20recruitment%20came%20from%20the%20same%20exam%20centre%20in%20Gwalior%2C%20a%20college%20run%20by%20a%20BJP%20MLA.%20Facing%20a%20demand%20by%20the%20Congress%20for%20a%20CBI%20inquiry%2C%20Chouhan%20in%20July%20put%20a%20stay%20on%20the%20appointment%20of%20the%20qualified%20candidates.%20The%20Congress%20chargesheet%20also%20includes%20allegations%20of%20irregularities%20in%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20mid-day%20meal%20scheme%2C%20Anganwadi%20department%2C%20distribution%20of%20tap%20water%2C%20para%20medical%20scholarship%2C%20sale%20of%20tribal%20land%2C%20illegal%20mining%20and%20the%20shoddy%20construction%20of%20the%20Mahakal%20Lok%20Corridor%20in%20Ujjain%2C%20where%20statues%20of%20Saptarishis%20were%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.news18.com%2Findia%2Fsix-saptarishi-statues-at-ujjain-mahakal-lok-collapse-spark-off-political-slugfest-7942189.html%23%5C%22%3Edamaged%3C%2Fa%3E%20due%20to%20gusty%20winds%20in%20May.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F26210023%2FF6uAo6VbgAAYzDa.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221117%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F26210023%2FF6uAo6VbgAAYzDa.jpeg%201117w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F26210023%2FF6uAo6VbgAAYzDa-300x157.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F26210023%2FF6uAo6VbgAAYzDa-1024x534.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-677021%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22583%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EShivraj%20Singh%20Chouhan.%20Photo%3A%20Twitter%2F%40ChouhanShivraj%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3ESaklecha%20says%20in%20addition%20to%20the%20long%20list%20of%20corruption%20charges%2C%20the%20concerning%20issue%20of%20unemployment%20and%20the%20manner%20in%20which%20the%20BJP%20overthrew%20the%20Congress%20government%20through%20the%20defection%20of%20almost%20two%20dozen%20MLAs%20in%202020%2C%20would%20play%20heavily%20in%20the%20minds%20of%20the%20voters.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%202018%2C%20the%20Congress%20caused%20a%20major%20upset%20as%20it%20emerged%20as%20the%20largest%20party%20in%20the%20MP%20assembly%2C%20winning%20114%20out%20of%20230%20seats.%20Though%20it%20fell%20short%20of%20a%20majority%2C%20it%20formed%20a%20government%20with%20the%20support%20of%20four%20independent%20MLAs%2C%20two%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party%20MLAs%20and%20one%20Samajwadi%20Party%20MLA.%20This%20mandate%2C%20read%20with%20the%20huge%20downward%20swing%20in%20the%20seat%20tally%20of%20the%20incumbent%20BJP%20from%20165%20to%20109%2C%20was%20an%20indication%20that%20the%20people%20voted%20to%20overthrow%20the%20BJP%20government%20after%2015%20years%20of%20its%20rule%2C%20says%20Saklecha.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20when%20the%20BJP%20formed%20the%20government%20again%20through%20defections%2C%20the%20voters%20felt%20cheated.%20There%20is%20huge%20anger%20among%20them%20regarding%20this%20betrayal.%20That%E2%80%99s%20why%20in%20this%20election%2C%20they%20will%20vote%20against%20BJP%20with%20twice%20the%20strength%20and%20hurt%20those%20who%20hurt%20their%20votes.%20This%20is%20going%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20Congress.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20issue%20of%20unemployment%20linked%20with%20the%20various%20irregularities%20in%20the%20recruitment%20process%20of%20various%20jobs%20has%20also%20put%20the%20Chouhan%20government%20on%20the%20back%20foot%20from%20time%20to%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20other%20whistle-blowers%20gained%20much%20of%20the%20limelight%20in%20highlighting%20irregularities%20in%20the%20Vyapam%20Scam%20in%202014%20and%202015%2C%20Saklecha%20was%20probably%20the%20first%20legislator%20to%20raise%20the%20subject%20in%20the%20state%20assembly%20way%20back%20in%202009.%20He%20was%20then%20an%20independent%20MLA.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20years%2C%20Saklecha%20has%20consistently%20filed%20RTIs%20and%20petitions%20and%20dug%20out%20key%20documents%20regarding%20the%20case%2C%20which%20is%20still%20being%20probed%20by%20the%20CBI.%20In%202015%2C%20he%20even%20published%20a%20100-page%20detailed%20summary%20of%20the%20scam%2C%20%E2%80%98%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fother-states%2FVyapam-scam-for-whistleblower-Paras-Saklecha-it-has-been-years-of-struggle%2Farticle60513093.ece%5C%22%3EVyapamgate%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%E2%80%99%20details%20from%20which%20were%20later%20used%20by%20the%20Congress%20to%20level%20corruption%20charges%20against%20Chouhan.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%202014%2C%20he%20submitted%20a%20340-page%20document%20to%20the%20CBI%20after%20the%20agency%20put%20out%20an%20advertisement%20asking%20the%20public%20who%20had%20complaints%20regarding%20the%20Vyapam%20recruitment%20scam%20to%20send%20documents%20and%20letters.%20However%2C%20nine%20years%20later%2C%20the%20scrutiny%20of%20his%20documents%20is%20still%20on%2C%20says%20Saklecha%2C%20who%20recently%20approached%20the%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20high%20court%20seeking%20information%20about%20the%20status%20of%20the%20probe.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGiven%20that%20Saklecha%20has%20a%20sound%20footing%20in%20finances%20and%20a%20record%20of%20raising%20corruption%20issues%20inside%20and%20outside%20the%20assembly%2C%20his%20candidature%20from%20Ratlam%20has%20drawn%20interest.%20The%20BJP%20won%20the%20Ratlam%20seat%20in%202013%20and%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESaklecha%20started%20out%20as%20a%20bank%20clerk%2C%20parallelly%20coaching%20students%20preparing%20for%20railways%20and%20bank%20exams.%20A%20gold%20medal%20winner%20in%20physics%20and%20a%20brilliant%20mathematician%E2%80%94his%20formulas%20are%20taught%20in%20the%20Hindi%20belt%E2%80%94Saklecha%20is%20also%20a%20poet%20and%20writer.%20In%201999%2C%20he%20was%20elected%20as%20the%20mayor%20of%20Ratlam%2C%20a%20result%20of%20his%20popularity%20for%20running%20free%20coaching%20centres%20for%20students.%20In%202003%2C%20he%20contested%20the%20assembly%20election%20for%20the%20first%20time%20but%20lost%20in%20a%20close%20fight%20to%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Himmat%20Kothari%2C%20who%20would%20go%20on%20to%20become%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20home%20minister.%20In%202008%2C%20Saklecha%20won%20his%20only%20election.%20In%202014%2C%20he%20contested%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20as%20an%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20candidate%20from%20Mandsaur%20but%20lost.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698056152000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F23153620%2Fcensored.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmadhya-pradesh-scams-bjp-congress-paras-saklecha%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Paras%20Saklecha%20is%20the%20Congress's%20candidate%20for%20the%20Ratlam%20constituency.%20He%20tells%20The%20Wire%20that%20corruption%20is%20among%20the%20top%20three%20issues%20that%20would%20count%20against%20the%20BJP%20government%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmadhya-pradesh-scams-bjp-congress-paras-saklecha%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Wim%20Wenders%2C%20Zhang%20Yimou%20Make%20Star%20Turns%20as%20Tokyo%20Film%20Festival%20Celebrates%20Reboot%20of%20International%20Relations%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698056139000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FZYM-at-TIFF-opening-GettyImages-1751748258-cr.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1235764711%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20dusk%20fell%20on%20a%20warm%20Tokyo%20evening%2C%20comeback%20director%20Wim%20Wenders%20introduced%20the%20cast%20and%20crew%20of%20%E2%80%9CPerfect%20Days%