-square-park-12990851%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20%26quot%3Bmasterpiece%26quot%3B%20sculpture%20has%20been%20unveiled%20in%20New%20York%20City%20paying%20homage%20to%20one%20of%20its%20most%20famous%20urban%20legends%20-%20alligators%20living%20in%20the%20sewers.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fnew-york-sculpture-commemorating-alligator-sewer-myth-unveiled-in-union-square-park-12990851%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fnew-york-sculpture-commemorating-alligator-sewer-myth-unveiled-in-union-square-park-12990851%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fnew-york-sculpture-commemorating-alligator-sewer-myth-unveiled-in-union-square-park-12990851%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22What%20To%20Make%20Of%20Rahul%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20Opposition%20to%20Digitisation%20of%20Land%20Records%20in%20Telangana%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F21211445%2FAadhaar-1200x560-1.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIndia%20is%20rapidly%20digitising.%20There%20are%20good%20things%20and%20bad%2C%20speed-bumps%20on%20the%20way%20and%20caveats%20to%20be%20mindful%20of.%20The%20weekly%20column%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cstrong%3ETerminal%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%C2%A0focuses%20on%20all%20that%20is%20connected%20and%20is%20not%20%E2%80%93%20on%20digital%20issues%2C%20policy%2C%20ideas%20and%20themes%20dominating%20the%20conversation%20in%20India%20and%20the%20world.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20issue%20of%20digitised%20land%20records%20has%20become%20an%20election%20issue%20in%20Telangana%20with%20the%20Congress%20and%20other%20opposition%20parties%20promising%20to%20shut%20down%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20land%20registry%20portal%2C%20%E2%80%9CDharani%E2%80%9D.%20The%20Congress%20has%20been%20very%20critical%20of%20land%20digitisation%2C%20saying%20that%20many%20farmers%20were%20affected%20by%20the%20error-prone%20process.%20In%20his%20recent%20visit%20to%20Telangana%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20promised%20to%20shut%20down%20the%20portal%20and%20claimed%20that%20digitisation%20was%20used%20as%20an%20excuse%20to%20take%20away%20agricultural%20lands%20for%20government%20projects.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDharani%20was%20made%20the%20only%20authentic%20source%20for%20land%20records%20in%202020%2C%20when%20Telangana%20passed%20a%20new%20revenue%20Act.%20The%20records%20on%20the%20land%20registry%20became%20mandatory%20for%20farmers%20to%20apply%20for%20crop%20loans%20and%20to%20receive%20direct%20benefit%20transfers%20under%20schemes%20like%20the%20Rythu%20Bandhu.%20Any%20error%20in%20recording%20the%20land%20details%20would%20harm%20a%20farmer%E2%80%99s%20ability%20to%20access%20welfare%20or%20participate%20in%20economic%20processes%20linked%20to%20land.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETelangana%20is%20the%20first%20state%20in%20India%20to%20push%20for%20the%20linking%20of%20land%20records%20to%20Aadhaar%20and%20digitise%20land%20records%20for%20a%20%E2%80%9Cpurified%E2%80%9D%20land%20registry.%20This%20process%20was%20challenged%20in%20the%20case%20of%20non-agricultural%20lands%20in%20the%20Telangana%20high%20court%2C%20which%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Fnews-updates%2Ftelangana-hc-directs-state-not-to-insist-aadhaar-for-uploading-property-details-165474%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Estopped%20Aadhaar%20linking%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Cspan%3Eto%20land%20records%20as%20it%20can%20only%20be%20allowed%20for%20subsidies%20and%20is%20in%20contravention%20with%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EPuttaswamy%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20judgment.%20As%20farmers%20with%20agricultural%20lands%20benefit%20from%20different%20welfare%20subsidies%2C%20the%20linking%20of%20Aadhaar%20and%20agricultural%20land%20records%20continues%20unopposed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20land%20digitisation%20process%20%E2%80%93%20like%20any%20other%20digitisation%20process%20%E2%80%93%20is%20prone%20to%20software%20and%20data%20errors%2C%20fraud%20and%20governance%20problems.%20This%20has%20been%20the%20case%20with%20Aadhaar%20for%20a%20decade%20and%20making%20any%20software%20mandatory%20and%20the%20only%20source%20of%20verifiable%20information%20has%20brought%20challenges%20to%20normal%20people.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20is%20a%20push%20for%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheprint.in%2Fopinion%2Fesign-can-do-to-land-markets-what-demat-did-to-equity-if-centre-and-state-come-together%2F1164167%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Edematerialisation%20of%20government%20documents%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20replacing%20them%20with%20centralised%20databases%20to%20facilitate%20easier%20market%20transactions.%20In%20the%20case%20of%20Dharani%2C%20this%20is%20done%20through%20the%20issual%20of%20an%20electronic%20record%20of%20the%20land%20title%20and%20giving%20access%20to%20this%20data%20to%20bankers%20and%20other%20market%20actors.%20Telangana%E2%80%99s%20new%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fadex.org.in%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EAgricultural%20Data%20Exchange%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20built%20in%20collaboration%20with%20IISc%20Bangalore%20and%20World%20Economic%20Forum%2C%20is%20a%20place%20where%20these%20ideas%20of%20data%20exchange%20with%20market%20actors%20to%20facilitate%20farmer%20and%20land%20data%20sharing%20are%20being%20carried%20out.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20recent%20research%20paper%20%E2%80%98%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fonlinelibrary.wiley.com%2Fdoi%2F10.1111%2Fjoac.12556%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EIllegibly%20legible%3A%20Outcomes%20of%20a%20land%20records%20modernisation%20programme%20in%20South%20India%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%98%3Cspan%3E%20by%20economists%20Ramkumar%20R.%20and%20Padmini%20Ramesh%20details%20the%20entire%20process%20of%20digitisation%20of%20land%20records%20for%20Dharani.%20It%20gives%20a%20historical%20background%20of%20the%20digitisation%20of%20land%20in%20Telangana%20and%20what%20kind%20of%20errors%20were%20encountered%20with%20the%20process%20and%20how%20the%20revenue%20department%20addresses%20these%20challenges.%20The%20paper%20captures%20the%20scale%20and%20intensity%20of%20problems%20encountered%20with%20Dharani.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESeveral%20complicated%20disputes%20around%20land%20records%20mutation%2C%20updation%2C%20errors%2C%20fraud%20and%20purity%20of%20land%20titles%20have%20risen.%20The%20corruption%20centred%20around%20land%20registrations%20is%20well%20known%20and%20the%20idea%20that%20digitisation%20will%20somehow%20fix%20this%20has%20become%20a%20myth%20for%20the%20regular%20farmer.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDharani%20has%20become%20an%20instrument%20where%20land%20titles%20automatically%20changed%20overnight%20with%20digitisation%2C%20not%20only%20due%20to%20errors%20or%20fraud%20by%20officials%20but%20also%20in%20scenarios%20where%20the%20state%20wanted%20to%20acquire%20land%20for%20development%20projects.%20In%20multiple%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanchronicle.com%2Fnation%2Fcurrent-affairs%2F251222%2Fkcrs-govt-to-face-farmers-anger-over-land-acquisition.html%5C%22%3Ereported%20incidents%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20Telangana%20government%20updated%20land%20records%20on%20Dharani%20to%20indicate%20farmers%E2%80%99%20land%20as%20belonging%20to%20the%20Telangana%20State%20Industrial%20and%20Infrastructure%20Corporation%20(TSIIC).%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F23135410%2FScreenshot-2023-10-23-at-1.45.01%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F23135410%2FScreenshot-2023-10-23-at-1.45.01%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F23135410%2FScreenshot-2023-10-23-at-1.45.01%25E2%2580%25AFPM-300x149.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F23135410%2FScreenshot-2023-10-23-at-1.45.01%25E2%2580%25AFPM-1024x509.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-681362%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22597%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20screengrab%20of%20the%20Dharani%20portal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWith%20digitisation%2C%20the%20state%20has%20the%20ability%20to%20arbitrarily%20change%20ownership%20of%20land%20and%20take%20it%20away%20with%20no%20recourse%20for%20the%20landowner.%20This%20ability%20needs%20to%20be%20seen%20in%20the%20context%20of.%20the%20Telangana%20government%20acquiring%20land%20while%20subverting%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flddashboard.legislative.gov.in%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2FA2013-30.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ethe%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Right%20To%20Fair%20Compensation%20And%20Transparency%20In%20Land%20Acquisition%2C%20Rehabilitation%20And%20Resettlement%20Act%2C%202013%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20to%20not%20pay%20fair%20compensation.%20This%20has%20been%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscroll.in%2Farticle%2F1037993%2Fhow-telangana-subverted-indias-land-acquisition-law%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eextensively%20written%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20about%20by%20Faustina%20Johnson.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETelangana%20chief%20minister%20K.%20Chandrashekhar%20Rao%20has%20been%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Ftelangana%2Fkcr-lambasts-detractors-of-dharani-asks-farmers-to-decide%2Farticle66939018.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ecountering%20the%20Congress%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20leaders%E2%80%99%20claims%20by%20assuring%20people%20that%20land%20records%20can%20only%20be%20changed%20with%20Aadhaar%20biometrics.%20All%20the%20land%20records%20of%20Dharani%20are%20supposed%20to%20be%20on%20a%20blockchain%2C%20according%20to%20various%20Telangana%20government%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fblockchaindistrict.telangana.gov.in%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ewebsites%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20However%2C%20there%20is%20no%20actual%20evidence%20this%20was%20carried%20out%20%E2%80%93%20as%20the%20current%20errors%20in%20the%20system%20show.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20role%20of%20Aadhaar%20in%20the%20land%20digitisation%20process%20is%20something%20of%20a%20mystery%20with%20no%20actual%20design%20details%20of%20the%20land%20registry%20available%20for%20anyone%20to%20understand%20the%20system.%20But%20what%20is%20not%20made%20clear%20to%20the%20general%20population%20is%20that%20Aadhaar%20usage%20is%20not%20actually%20used%20for%20identification%2C%20authentication%20or%20updation%20through%20eKYC.%20Instead%2C%20an%20Aadhaar-based%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcca.gov.in%2FeSign.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ee-Sign%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20is%20being%20used%20to%20digitally%20sign%20the%20land%20records%20before%20patta%20passbooks%20are%20issued%20through%20Dharani.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20important%20to%20understand%20how%20the%20e-Sign%20system%20itself%20functions%20and%20what%20safeguards%20are%20being%20provided%20to%20citizens.%20The%20Aadhaar-based%20biometric%20authentication%20system%20is%20broken%2C%20with%20people%20able%20to%20clone%20biometrics%20and%20use%20Aadhaar%20authentication%20to%20commit%20fraudulent%20withdrawals%20by%20using%20the%20Aadhaar%20Enabled%20Payment%20System%20(AEPS).%20It%20is%20not%20just%20the%20state%20that%20can%20take%20away%20land%20%E2%80%93%20anyone%20with%20access%20to%20the%20land%20registry%20with%20details%20of%20your%20Aadhaar%20number%20and%20biometrics%20can%20potentially%20take%20your%20land%20away.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWith%20the%20Registration%20of%20Births%20and%20Deaths%20Act%20making%20Aadhaar%20mandatory%20for%20property%20registration%2C%20this%20process%20is%20going%20to%20be%20scaled%20across%20India.%20Aadhaar%20is%20being%20shown%20as%20a%20way%20to%20handle%20estate%20management%20of%20claims%20over%20property%20after%20the%20death%20of%20an%20individual.%20It%20is%20unclear%20how%20this%20will%20happen%20at%20this%20stage.%20In%20the%20case%20of%20Dharani%20too%2C%20the%20details%20of%20dependents%20of%20the%20property%20owner%20were%20collected%20to%20facilitate%20estate%20transfer.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20promise%20of%20the%20immutability%20of%20land%20records%20that%20has%20been%20guaranteed%20in%20the%20form%20of%20blockchain%2C%20cleaning%20up%20and%20purifying%20records%20with%20Aadhaar%20linking%20are%20all%20technological%20myths%20if%20the%20systems%20are%20broken%20by%20design%20with%20tall%20claims%20that%20don%E2%80%99t%20hold%20up.%20Indians%20deserve%20a%20better%20digitisation%20process%20with%20actual%20accountability%20instead%20of%20mere%20claims.%20While%20the%20Congress%20always%20defended%20Aadhaar%20for%20welfare%2C%20it%20now%20seems%20to%20have%20caught%20on%20to%20other%20issues%20of%20the%20digitisation%20process.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fskodali%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ESrinivas%20Kodali%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%20is%20a%20researcher%20on%20digitisation%20and%20a%20hacktivist.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698049857000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F21211445%2FAadhaar-1200x560-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Frahul-gandhi-digitised-land-records-telangana%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Despite%20tall%20claims%20about%20purity%20of%20records%2C%20the%20Dharani%20land%20registry%20portal%20has%20been%20riddled%20with%20errors%20and%20cases%20of%20fraud.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Frahul-gandhi-digitised-land-records-telangana%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Vijay%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Leo%E2%80%99%20Beats%20Leonardo%20DiCaprio%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Killers%20of%20the%20Flower%20Moon%E2%80%99%20at%20Weekend%20Global%20Box%20Office%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698049605000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FLeo-poster.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1235764650%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Lokesh%20Kanagaraj%E2%80%99s%20Tamil-language%20%E2%80%9CLeo%3A%20Bloody%20Sweet%2C%E2%80%9D%20starring%20Vijay%2C%20debuted%20in%20third%20position%20at%20the%20global%20box%20office%20over%20the%20latest%20weekend%2C%20with%20%2431.2%20million%20planetwide%2C%20according%20to%20estimates%20released%20on%20Sunday%20by%20Comscore.%20The%20weekend%20was%20won%20by%20Martin%20Scorsese%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9CKillers%20of%20the%20Flower%20Moon%2C%E2%80%9D%20starring%20Leonardo%20DiCaprio%2C%20Robert%20De%20Niro%20and%20Lily%20Gladstone%2C%20with%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2023%2Ffilm%2Fnews%2Fvijay-leo-global-box-office-1235764650%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fvariety.com%2F2023%2Ffilm%2Fnews%2Fvijay-leo-global-box-office-1235764650%2Famp%2F%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2023%2Ffilm%2Fnews%2Fvijay-leo-global-box-office-1235764650%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%2