-temple-premises-tdb%2Farticleshow%2F100438945.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Eactivities%20organised%20by%20the%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%3C%2Fa%3E%20(RSS)%20on%20their%20premises.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20this%20restriction%20is%20already%20in%20place%2C%20the%20board%20issued%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fthiruvananthapuram%2Fno-rss-drills-on-temple-premises-tdb%2Farticleshow%2F100438945.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Efresh%20directive%20reiterating%20the%20ban%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20reports%20of%20RSS%20activities%20happening%20in%20a%20few%20temples%20in%20Kerala%20surfaced.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20circular%20issued%20by%20the%20board%20clarified%20that%20other%20than%20temple%20festivals%20and%20rituals%2C%20the%20premises%20should%20not%20be%20used%20for%20other%20purposes%20and%20officers%20who%20fail%20to%20comply%20with%20this%20order%20may%20face%20strict%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Left%20Democratic%20Front%20(LDF)%20government%20had%20expressed%20their%20opposition%20to%20RSS%20using%20temple%20premises%20for%20their%20physical%20training%20that%20sometimes%20involve%20weapons.%20Chief%20minister%20Pinrayi%20Vijayan%20had%20criticised%20the%20right-wing%20paramilitary%20organisation%20for%20using%20the%20temple%20premises%20for%20their%20%3Cem%3Eshakhas%3C%2Fem%3E%20(branches)%20and%20physical%20training%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3ETimes%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fthiruvananthapuram%2Fno-rss-drills-on-temple-premises-tdb%2Farticleshow%2F100438945.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20temple%20board%20said%20that%20not%20just%20the%20RSS%2C%20but%20other%20organisations%20and%20political%20parties%20will%20also%20not%20be%20allowed%20to%20use%20temple%20premises%20for%20other%20purposes.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20deputy%20commissioners%2C%20assistant%20commissioners%2C%20administrative%20officers%20and%20sub-group%2