ormer%20generals%20alone.%20The%20Islamabad%20High%20court%20subsequently%20granted%20Nawaz%20Sharif%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Fpakistan-nawaz-sharif-return-court-bail-338969ba6aaa248ca4c983244a4f51b9%5C%22%3Eprotective%20bail%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Stage%20was%20finally%20set%20for%20grand%20old%20man%20of%20Pakistani%20politics%20to%20return%20home.%20And%20when%20Nawaz%20Sharif%20finally%20delivered%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dawn.com%2Fnews%2F1782790%5C%22%3Ehomecoming%20speech%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20a%20very%20large%20and%20emotionally-charged%20crowd%20at%20the%20Minar-e-Pakistan%2C%20Lahore%2C%20he%20kept%20it%20circumspect.%20He%20alluded%20indirectly%20to%20the%20orchestrators%20of%20his%20ouster%20by%20asking%20who%20are%20the%20ones%20who%20keep%20coming%20between%20him%20and%20the%20people%3F%20Sharif%20made%20it%20a%20point%20to%20say%20that%20he%20had%20no%20wish%20for%20revenge%2C%20and%20that%20his%20only%20aim%20was%20to%20give%20relief%20to%20the%20people.%20He%20called%20for%20all%20institutions%20to%20work%20together.%20But%20hinting%20that%20he%20still%20can%20raise%20hell%20if%20pushed%20around%2C%20Nawaz%20Sharif%20recited%20a%20famous%20verse%20by%20Ghalib%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EGh%C4%81lib%20hame%C3%B1%20nah%20chhe%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3E%E1%B9%9B%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3E%20kih%20phir%20josh-e%20ashk%20se%3Cbr%3E%20bai%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3E%E1%B9%AD%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3Ehe%20hai%C3%B1%20ham%20tah%C4%AByah-e%20t%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3E%CC%A4%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3E%C5%AB%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3Ef%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3E%C4%81%C3%B1%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3E%20kiye%20hu%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3E%CA%BE%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3Ee%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffranpritchett.com%2F00ghalib%2F233%2F233_17.html%5C%22%3EGhalib%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20don%E2%80%99t%20tease%2Ftorment%20us%2C%20for%20again%20with%2Fthrough%20a%20turmoil%20of%20tears%3Cbr%3E%20we%20are%20settled%2Fbrooding%2C%20having%20made%20provision%2Farrangement%20for%2