%3EAll%20India%20Kisan%20Sabha%20in%20Maharashtra%20in%202018%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%3B%20second%2C%20when%20they%20marched%20from%20different%20parts%20of%20the%20country%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Ffarmers-protest-singhu-charity-farewell%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Etowards%20the%20Delhi%20border%20in%202020%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%3B%20and%20lastly%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbharat-jodo-yatra-public-action-congress%5C%22%3E%20%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EBharat%20Jodo%20Yatra%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Ein%202022%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20all%20three%20cases%2C%20leaders%20and%20masses%20walked%20hundreds%20and%20thousands%20of%20miles%20across%20the%20length%20and%20breadth%20of%20the%20country.%20Let%20us%20understand%20the%20way%20walking%20gets%20employed%20as%20a%20political%20instrument%20with%20contemporary%20examples.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20walk%20everyday%20and%20our%20socio-economic%20and%20cultural%20context%20determines%20the%20nature%20of%20our%20walking%20%E2%80%93%20from%20a%20worker%20walking%20to%20their%20workplace%2C%20trying%20to%20make%20ends%20meet%2C%20to%20the%20relatively%20better%20off%20population%20walking%20to%20take%20care%20of%20their%20life-style%20diseases.%20They%20do%20not%20grab%20our%20attention%20the%20way%20the%20farmers%20or%20Rahul%20did.%20Attention%20was%20due%20to%20the%20political%20noise%20it%20was%20making.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWalking%20as%20a%20political%20project%20had%20ceased%20to%20be%20part%20of%20political%20imagination%20except%20in%20cases%20of%20parties%20organising%20marches%20in%20a%20few%20states.%20That%20is%20why%20the%20Maharashtra%20farmers%E2%80%99%20march%20and%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Yatra%20stand%20out.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20current%C2%A0%20political%20climate%2C%20walking%20as%20a%20political%20project%20is%20new%2C%20abnormal%20and%20under-explored.%20Primary%20reason%20being%20the%20political%20illusion%20of%20%E2%80%98reaching%E2%80%99%20people%20online%20understood%20as%20%E2%80%98knowing%E2%80%99%20people%20and%20the%20society%20in%20actuality.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EImages%20posted%20on%20online%20forums%20and%20the%20likes%20collected%20%E2%80%93%20representing%20their%20pains%2C%20angst%20and%20anxieties%20%E2%80%93%20killed%20the%20significance%20of%20physical%20connection.%20Secondly%2C%20the%20dominant%20politics%20constructs%20a%20self-image%20that%20being%20physically%20distant%20from%20people%20implies%20being%20more%20powerful.%20The%20more%20inaccessible%20the%20leader%20is%2C%20the%20more%20powerful%20he%20is%20assumed%20to%20be.%20Hence%2C%20the%20political%20leadership%20develops%20a%20host%20of%20paraphernalia%20to%20limit%20access.%20There%20is%20celebration%20of%20being%20distant%20from%20the%20masses%20in%20physical%20form.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EWalking%20as%20a%20political%20tool%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20was%20not%20always%20like%20this.%20Irrespective%20of%20political%20agreements%20and%20disagreements%20within%20the%20Congress%20leadership%2C%20we%20saw%20how%20Nehru%20had%20no%20qualms%20mixing%20with%20the%20masses%2C%20Indira%20Gandhi%20lessened%20it%2C%20and%20then%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%20was%20killed%20as%20he%20was%20nonchalant%20about%20physical%20meetings.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThereafter%2C%20there%20was%20a%20lull%20within%20the%20party%20as%20the%20leaders%20began%20to%20physically%20distance%20themselves%20from%20the%20masses.%20This%20happened%20simultaneously%20with%20the%20disappearance%20of%20mass%20mobilisation%20as%20a%20tool%20of%20politics%20within%20the%20party.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENehru%20emerged%20from%20a%20history%20of%20anti-colonial%20struggle%20and%20mobilisations%20which%20defined%20his%20relationship%20of%20physical%20contact%20with%20masses.%20This%20historical%20characterisation%20of%20subsequent%20Gandhi%20family%20leaders%20was%20much%20less%20in%20comparison%20and%20hence%2C%20their%20physical%20relationship%20with%20the%20masses%20decreased.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20party%20emerging%20as%20a%20powerful%20political%20force%20post-independence%20was%20a%20result%20of%20mass%20mobilisation%20with%20the%20Nehru-Gandhi%20family%20at%20its%20centre.%20That%20memory%20of%20connection%20with%20the%20masses%20lingered%20on%20for%20a%20few%20decades.%20The%20disconnect%20with%20the%20masses%20happened%20as%20the%20necessity%20of%20addressing%20newly%20emerging%20political%20necessities%20were%20ignored.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbharat-jodo-yatra-achievement-goals%5C%22%3EHas%20the%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Yatra%20Achieved%20What%20It%20Set%20Out%20to%20Do%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20political%20agency%20of%20the%20marginalised%20caste%20groups%20began%20knocking%20at%20the%20doors%20of%20established%20political%20forces%2C%20parties%20such%20as%20the%20Congress%2C%20due%20to%20the%20entrenched%20Brahmanical%20interests%2C%20lagged%20in%20responding%20to%20the%20issues%20at%20an%20organisational%20level.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20reason%20was%20that%20they%20paid%20less%20attention%20to%20the%20evolving%20turmoil%20in%20the%20social%20and%20economic%20order%20on%20the%20ground%20as%20the%20political%20nostalgia%20of%20the%20freedom%20struggle%20and%20the%20Nehruvian%20years%20were%20thought%20sufficient%20for%20electoral%20gains.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EChallenges%20appeared%20in%20different%20regions%20from%20the%20emerging%20movements%20and%20identitarian%20assertion%20on%20the%20ground.%20And%20the%20Congress%20party%20did%20not%20have%20an%20organisational%20structure%20with%20an%20inclusive%2C%20non-patronising%20framework.%20This%20began%20weakening%20the%20political%20strength%20of%20the%20Congress.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20Rahul%20arrived%20on%20the%20scene%2C%20the%20disjunct%20between%20the%20actuality%20and%20projections%20in%20the%20virtual%20sphere%20had%20already%20created%20an%20illusion%20unheard%20of.%20This%20disjunct%20hid%20the%20actuality%20%E2%80%93%20the%20exploitation%2C%20marginalisation%2C%20deprivation%2C%20violence%2C%20hunger%20and%20death%20as%20experienced%20by%20people%20on%20the%20ground.%20Absence%20of%20a%20robust%20cadre-based%20organisation%2C%20which%20right-wing%20politics%20has%2C%20implied%20that%20the%20leadership%20had%20to%20give%20a%20call.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20a%20long%20time%2C%20Rahul%20has%20decided%20to%20plunge%20himself%20in%20the%20political%20format%20that%20congress%20leaders%20of%20pre-independence%20India%20practiced.%20He%20is%20trying%20to%20imbibe%20the%20mode%20of%20being%20a%20mass%20leader%20which%20is%20unlike%20any%20other%20political%20leader%20at%20the%20moment.%20His%20recent%20political%20activities%20have%20been%20efforts%20at%20establishing%20that%C2%A0%20democracy%20(even%20in%20its%20liberal%20format)%20is%20about%20the%20relationship%20between%20political%20parties%2C%C2%A0%20the%20masses%20and%20the%20state%20as%20their%20representatives.%20He%20is%20reimagining%20an%20idea%20of%20state-people%20relationship%20as%20an%20alternative%20to%20whatever%20has%20transpired%20in%20the%20past%20few%20decades.%20This%20relationship%20is%20more%20than%20mere%20voting%20but%20it%20is%20about%20listening%20to%20the%20masses%2C%20understanding%20their%20feelings%20first%20hand%20and%20expressing%20solidarity%20with%20them.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ESpectacularity%20as%20a%20substitute%20of%20conversationality%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20have%20a%20history%20replete%20with%20people%20who%20walked%20and%20learned%20the%20lessons%20of%20life%20and%20politics%20%E2%80%93%20from%20Gautam%20Buddha%2C%20Guru%20Nanak%20to%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20and%20Khan%20Abdul%20Gaffar%20Khan%20among%20many%20others.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThat%20history%20has%20been%20delegitimised%20by%20the%20contemporary%20politicians%20who%20attend%20five%20meetings%20on%20the%20same%20day%20in%20different%20parts%20of%20the%20country%20using%20sponsored%20modes%20of%20transport.%20Walking%20as%20a%20mode%20of%20politics%20has%20been%20virtually%20ignored.%20Walking%20brings%20freedom%3B%20it%20liberates%20one%20from%20all%20that%20is%20ongoing%2C%20it%20separates%20you%20from%20the%20narcissism%20and%20the%20comforts%20of%20the%20echo-chamber%2C%20prompts%20you%20to%20think%20afresh%20and%20provides%20fodder%20to%20reflect%20anew.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20this%20sense%2C%20walking%20is%20also%20about%20meeting%20people%20and%20being%20alone%20and%20contemplating%2C%20all%20at%20the%20same%20time.%20By%20walking%20one%20surrender%E2%80%99s%20one%E2%80%99s%20own%20identity%20and%20meets%20people%20from%20different%20quarters%20of%20life%20where%20the%20privileges%20bestowed%20by%20your%20identity%20do%20not%20infringe%20upon%20your%20life.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20hegemonic%20forces%20have%20created%20an%20illusory%20reality%20through%20virtual%20presence.%20Across%20organisations%20chief%20ministers%20have%20their%20faces%20everywhere%20%E2%80%93%20from%20toilets%2C%20sewage%20cleaning%20machines%2C%20newspapers%2C%20hoardings%20to%20buses%20and%20rickshaws.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F10144549%2FLead-image-size-1.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F10144549%2FLead-image-size-1.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F10144549%2FLead-image-size-1-300x134.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F10144549%2FLead-image-size-1-1024x457.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-672389%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22535%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20on%20a%20G20%20poster.%20Photo%3A%20Shukla%20Sawant%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20phenomenon%20picked%20up%20as%20political%20leadership%20decided%20to%20fill%20the%20minds%C2%A0%20of%20people%20with%20their%20own%20personal%20images.%20The%20photograph%20of%20the%20leader%20represents%20the%20politics%20rather%20than%20the%20content%20of%20politics.%20Therefore%2C%20the%20emphasis%20is%20to%20construct%20the%20image.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20further%20contributes%20to%20distancing%20of%20politics%20from%20the%20masses%20and%20an%20inflated%20sense%20of%20self%20in%20political%20leaders%20seeing%20themselves%20everywhere.%20In%20such%20a%20situation%2C%20detachment%20becomes%20a%20necessity%20to%20think%20clearly.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EDetachment%20from%20the%20virtual%20world%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20political%20habitat%20comprises%20paraphernalia%20of%20different%20kinds%20%E2%80%93%20from%20cameras%20surrounding%20you%20at%20all%20times%20to%20a%20possibly%20sanitised%20space.%20This%20constrains%20the%20physical%20and%2C%20therefore%2C%20mental%20movement%20of%20the%20politician.%20When%20Gandhi%20and%20Nehru%20and%20the%20farmers%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0walked%2C%20they%20were%20unconstrained.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EToday%20the%20politicians%20walk%20on%20cleanly%20lined%20carpers%20at%20temples%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eand%20even%20in%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Felections%2Flok-sabha-elections%2Flok-sabha-election-news%2Fas-campaign-ends-pm-modi-walks-kedarnath-red-carpet%2Farticleshow%2F69392395.cms%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eremote%20places%20in%20the%20Himalayas%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20They%20are%20welcomed%20by%20a%20set%20of%20people%20they%20already%20know%20and%20who%20speak%20predetermined%20dialogues.%20Masses%20are%20cordoned%20off%20to%20inaccessibly%20far%20off%20places%20in%20a%20public%20meeting%20and%20even%20those%20who%20shower%20petals%20are%20recruited%20and%20trained.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20world%20of%20lies%20and%20illusion.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20recent%20past%2C%20mainstream%20political%20leaders%20have%20seldom%20walked%20across%20the%20length%20and%20breadth%20of%20their%20own%20electoral%20constituency%2C%C2%A0%20let%20alone%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20country.%20Riding%20on%20the%20technical%20crutches%20of%20social%20media%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20even%20meet%20their%20voters.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20are%20people%20who%20haven%E2%80%99t%20met%20either%20municipality%2C%20assembly%20or%20parliamentary%20candidates%20of%20their%20area.%20The%20distance%20between%20the%20leader%20and%20the%20masses%20has%20been%20increasing%2C%20filled%20through%20intermediaries%20of%20technology.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20has%20been%20an%20impersonalisation%20of%20politics%2C%20democracy%20being%20redefined.%20Prime%20ministers%2C%20chief%20ministers%20do%20roadshows.%20The%20roadshows%20are%20instruments%20of%20spectacularity.%20In%20a%20time%20when%20masses%20are%20being%20served%20a%20larger%20than%20life%20image%20of%20politicians%2C%20the%20roadshows%20are%20mere%20attempts%20at%20shortcutting%20the%20processes%20of%20democracy%20%E2%80%93%20a%20glimpse%20of%20who%20they%20elect%20instead%20of%20a%20conversation%20or%20touch.%20This%20process%20alienates%20masses%20from%20politics%20and%20takes%20away%20the%20dialogic%20relationship%20between%20the%20masses%20and%20politicians.%20In%20the%20long%20run%20this%20results%20in%20a%20disconnect%20of%20political%20forces%20with%20the%20real%20issues%2C%20needs%20and%20aspirations%20of%20the%20masses.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20a%20sanitised%20stage%20the%20political%20persona%20is%20bereft%20of%20human%20interface.%20It%20gets%20alienated%20from%20the%20public%2C%20from%20the%20realities%20of%20its%20constituents.%20To%20take%20care%20of%20the%20consequent%20chasm%20between%20the%20political%20persona%20and%20the%20masses%2C%20spectacularisation%20of%20political%20relationships%20is%20employed.%20Politics%20is%20transformed%20into%20a%20spectacle%20and%20so%20is%20the%20body%20and%20the%20self%20of%20the%20politician.%20This%20gets%20expressed%20through%20images%20%E2%80%93%20still%20as%20well%20as%20moving.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHence%2C%20the%20full%20control%20over%20agencies%20that%20transmit%20images%20is%20intended%20and%20undertaken.%20French%20philosopher%20Guy%20Debord%20tells%20us%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20images%20detached%20from%20every%20aspect%20of%20life%20merge%20into%20a%20common%20stream%20in%20which%20the%20unity%20of%20that%20life%20can%20no%20longer%20be%20recovered.%20Fragmented%20views%20of%20reality%20regroup%20themselves%20into%20a%20new%20unity%20as%20a%20separate%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3Epseudo-world%20that%20can%20only%20be%20looked%20at.%20The%20specialisation%20of%20images%20of%20the%20world%20evolves%20into%20a%20world%20of%20autonomised%20images%20where%20even%20the%20deceivers%20are%20deceived.%20The%20spectacle%20is%20a%20concrete%20inversion%20of%20life%2C%20an%20autonomous%20movement%20of%20the%20non-living%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIncreasing%20absence%20of%20control%20over%20social%20media%2C%20generally%20employed%20to%20take%20care%20of%20the%20above%20mentioned%20chasm%2C%20often%20gets%20employed%20against%20the%20producers%20of%20those%20memes%20and%20messages%20themselves.%20Only%20a%20political%20counter-narrative%20that%20brings%20people%20in%20flesh%20and%20blood%20to%20the%20centre%20of%20politics%20can%20deal%20with%20this%20spectacularisation.%20There%20can%20be%20different%20kinds%20of%20counter-narratives%20depending%20on%20how%20the%20material%20conditions%20are%20understood%20and%20the%20kind%20of%20politics%20that%20is%20imagined%20to%20transform%20those%20material%20conditions.%20Rahul%E2%80%99s%20recent%20initiatives%20can%20be%20seen%20as%20a%20move%20in%20that%20direction.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EWalking%20to%20what%20end%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20does%20Rahul%20seek%20to%20attain%20through%20his%20marches%20and%20through%20walks%20within%20villages%20and%20in%20fields%3F%20No%20doubt%2C%20it%20can%20be%20debated%20that%20these%20actions%20are%20embedded%20in%20the%20consumptive%20framework%20of%20a%20certain%20kind%2C%20as%20it%20gets%20edited%20and%20then%20presented%20to%20viewers%20while%20simultaneously%20providing%20an%20unedited%2C%20raw%20version%20as%20well.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20act%20of%20walking%20through%20villages%2C%20on%20non-sanitised%2C%20non-carpeted%20streets%2C%20roads%20and%20temple%20paths%20is%20counter-positioning%20of%20an%20alternative%20politics%20to%20the%20current%20narrative%20of%20sanitised%2C%20carpeted%20and%20well-scripted%20mingling%20with%20masses.%20How%20far%20will%20this%20narrative%20embed%20all%20this%20in%20the%20politico-economic%20and%20materiality%20of%20societies%20is%20a%20separate%20question.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20Rahul%20spends%20time%20with%20different%20kinds%20of%20people%2C%20he%20extricates%20himself%20out%20of%20the%20superficiality%20of%20the%20discourse%20woven%20by%20the%20social%20media%20and%20interacts%20with%20the%20actual%20people%20in%20flesh%20and%20blood%2C%20reflecting%20on%20their%20conditions%20and%20conversations%20he%20had%20with%20them.%20This%20walk%20liberates%20one%20from%20the%20repetition%20of%20images%20generated%20within%20the%20confines%20of%20the%20city%20and%20the%20ecosystem%20created%20by%20the%20hegemonic%20powers.%20That%20ecosystem%20of%20constantly%20thinking%20that%20tweeting-means-meeting-people%20is%20breached%2C%20new%20images%20get%20built%2C%20which%20might%20produce%20a%20completely%20different%20political%20persona%20and%20a%20politics.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20this%20situation%2C%20the%20significance%20of%20undoing%20the%20sanitised%20sphere%20of%20politics%20becomes%20significant.%20It%20acquires%20the%20status%20of%20a%20counter-agenda%2C%20as%20a%20necessity%20that%20claims%20to%20disturb%20the%20autocracy%20of%20the%20sanitised%20and%20spectacularised%20space%20that%20the%20right-wing%20neoliberal%20politics%20creates.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ERavi%20Kumar%20teaches%20Sociology%20at%20South%20Asian%20University.%20Views%20expressed%20in%20this%20article%20are%20personal.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698028249000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F02%2F08132916%2FFnjeMatacAMewxT.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fwalking-as-political-tool-in-contemporary-india%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20the%20current%C2%A0political%20climate%2C%20walking%20as%20a%20political%20project%20is%20new%2C%20abnormal%20and%20under-explored%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A19%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fwalking-as-political-tool-in-contemporary-india%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Philippines%20tells%20China%20to%20stop%20provocative%20actions%20in%20South