s%20of%20humanitarian%20aid%20into%20Gaza%2C%20but%20UNICEF%20described%20this%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bdrop%20in%20the%20ocean%26quot%3B%20considering%20the%20situation%20in%20the%20Strip.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EOver%2040%20per%20cent%20of%20housing%20in%20Gaza%20has%20been%20damaged%20or%20destroyed%2C%20a%20UN%20report%20said%2C%20quoting%20local%20authorities.%20More%20than%20half%20of%20Gaza's%20population%20has%20been%20displaced%20due%20to%20the%20airstrikes%20in%20the%20densely%20populated%20Strip.%20With%20sanitation%20facilities%20hit%20by%20Israel's%20blockade%20on%20supplies%2C%20cases%20of%20chicken%20pox%2C%20scabies%20and%20diarrhea%20are%20being%20reported%2C%20the%20UN%20has%20said.%C2%A0The%20UN%20has%20called%20for%20an%20immediate%20end%20to%20violence.%20%26quot%3BGaza%20was%20a%20desperate%20humanitarian%20situation%20before%20the%20most%20recent%20hostilities.%20It%20is%20now%20catastrophic.%20The%20world%20must%20do%20more%2C%26quot%3B%20five%20UN%20bodies%20have%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3C%2Fol%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697962440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fu4ru77ko_gaza-devastation_625x300_22_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-gaza-war-israel-hamas-war-gaza-braces-for-more-fire-as-israel-removes-risks-before-ground-offensive-4504355%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20humanitarian%20crisis%20in%20Gaza%20is%20set%20to%20worsen%20as%20Israel%20gears%20up%20to%20intensify%20airstrikes%20to%20prepare%20the%20ground%20for%20an%20all-out%20ground%20offensive.%20Hamas'%20attack%20on%20Israel%20and%20the%20retaliation%20has%20claimed%20nearly%205%2C800%20lives%20so%20far%2C%20UN%20estimates%20say.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-gaza-war-israel-hamas-war-gaza-braces-for-more-fire-as-israel-removes-risks-before-ground-offensive-4504355%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3