%20with%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%2C%20Samajwadi%20Party%20Chief%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20has%20put%20out%20a%20post%20on%20social%20media%20which%20has%20raised%20eyebrows%20for%20reverting%20to%20his%20'PDA'%20coinage%20and%20leaving%20out%20any%20mention%20of%20the%20opposition%20alliance.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETies%20between%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20and%20the%20Congress%20have%20been%20strained%20since%20the%20latter%20left%20no%20seats%20for%20its%20INDIA%20ally%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20despite%20allegedly%20assuring%20the%20SP%20that%20it%20would%20consider%20its%20candidates%20for%20six%20constituencies.%20A%20fuming%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20has%20been%20hitting%20out%20at%20the%20Congress%20since%20then%20and%20the%20two%20parties%20have%20ended%20up%20fielding%20candidates%20against%20each%20other%20on%2018%20constituencies%20in%20the%20state%2C%20which%20will%20vote%20for%20the%20Assembly%20elections%20on%20November%2017.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20post%20on%20X%2C%20formerly%20Twitter%2C%20on%20Sunday%2C%20Mr%20Yadav%20shared%20a%20photo%20of%20an%20SP%20worker%20with%20his%20back%20coloured%20in%20the%20party's%20signature%20red-and-green%20and%20a%20message%20written%20on%20it%20in%20Hindi.%20The%20message%20reads.%20%26quot%3BMission%202024.%20May%20Netaji%20(late%20Mulayam%20Singh%20Yadav)%20remain%20immortal.%20'PDA'%20will%20ensure%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20wins%20the%20election%20this%20time.%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20will%20ensure%20the%20poor%20get%20justice.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22hi%5C%22%3E%E0%A4%B9%E0%A5%8B%E0%A4%97%E0%A4%BE%2024%20%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%BE%20%E0%A4%9A%E0%A5%81%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%B5%3Cbr%3E%20PDA%20%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%BE%20%E0%A4%87%E0%A4%82%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%BC%E0%A4%B2%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%AC%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FK7RUPKPxl6%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FK7RUPKPxl6%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%E2%80%94%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20(%40yadav