.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fisrael-hamas-war-at-least-55-palestinians-killed-in-overnight-israeli-airstrikes-on-gaza-and-the-west-bank-12989837%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fisrael-hamas-war-at-least-55-palestinians-killed-in-overnight-israeli-airstrikes-on-gaza-and-the-west-bank-12989837%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Saudi%20Prince's%20Takedown%20Of%20Israel%2C%20Hamas%20Over%20Gaza%20War%20Mentions%20India%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20powerful%20remarks%20on%20the%20ongoing%20war%20in%20Gaza%2C%20a%20Saudi%20Arabia%20prince%2C%20who%20was%20the%20country's%20former%20intelligence%20chief%2C%20has%20slammed%20both%20Hamas%20and%20Israel%20and%20said%20there%20are%20%26quot%3Bno%20heroes%20in%20this%20conflict%2C%20only%20victims%26quot%3B.%20Turki%20Al%20Faisal's%20speech%20at%20a%20US%20university%20also%20mentions%20India%20when%20he%20cites%20the%20example%20of%20the%20Independence%20movement%20as%20an%20example%20of%20resisting%20occupation%20through%20civil%20disobedience.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20viral%20video%20of%20the%20address%20starts%20with%20the%2078-year-old%20saying%20that%20all%20occupied%20people%20have%20a%20right%20to%20resist%20their%20occupation%2C%20even%20militarily.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20do%20not%20support%20the%20military%20option%20in%20Palestine.%20I%20prefer%20the%20other%20option%3A%20civil%20insurrection%20and%20disobedience.%20It%20brought%20down%20the%20British%20empire%20in%20India%20and%20the%20Soviet%20empire%20in%20eastern%20Europe%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EHis%20Royal%20Highness%20Prince%20Turki%20Al%20Faisal%20Al%20Saud%2C%20former%20Ambassador%20of%20Saudi%20Arabia%20to%20the%20U.S.%2C%20gives%20his%20perspective.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FBakerLive%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23BakerLive%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href