Cem%3Ekulhads%3C%2Fem%3E.%20With%20glass%20cups%2C%20the%20hygiene%20quotient%20is%20really%20low%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20way%20these%20glass%20cups%20are%20usually%20washed%20is%20by%20dipping%20them%20in%20soap%20water%20and%20then%20once%20in%20clean%20water.%20And%20with%20this%2C%20they%20are%20ready%20for%20another%20use.%20I%20always%20preferred%20%3Cem%3Ekulhad%20%3C%2Fem%3Eover%20glass%2C%20or%20even%20paper%20cups.%20My%20friends%20would%20prefer%20to%20pay%20more%20for%20%3Cem%3Ekulhad%20%3C%2Fem%3Echai%20due%20to%20its%20hygienic%20and%20environmental%20reasons%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fkulhad--1697721762.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Shobhit%20has%20helped%2045%20plants%20to%20be%20set%20up%20in%20different%20parts%20of%20the%20country%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fkulhad--1697721762.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fkulhad--1697721762-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fkulhad--1697721762-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fkulhad--1697721762-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fkulhad--1697721762-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-332621%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EShobhit%20has%20helped%2045%20plants%20to%20be%20set%20up%20in%20different%20parts%20of%20the%20country.%20Picture%20credit%3A%20Shobhit%20Soni%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20gave%20rise%20to%20Shobhit%E2%80%99s%20startup%20idea%