e%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20plan%20comes%20with%20complete%20information%20on%20setting%20up%20of%20the%20plant.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20video%20got%20a%20lot%20of%20views%20and%20people%20started%20to%20reach%20out%20to%20me.%20The%20%3Cem%3Edesi%20%3C%2Fem%3Eway%20of%20making%20%3Cem%3Ekulhad%20%3C%2Fem%3Eis%20by%20hand%2C%20but%20I%20have%20developed%20a%20machine%20to%20do%20the%20same.%20When%20a%20customer%20comes%20to%20us%2C%20we%20help%20them%20set%20up%20their%20factory%2C%20give%20them%20the%20machine%20and%20also%20train%20them%20in%20using%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20costs%20the%20people%20only%20about%20a%20percent%20of%20what%20Shobhit%20spent%20on%20setting%20up%20his%20plant.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20watching%20the%20videos%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20aspiring%20people%20come%20to%20us%20to%20learn%20the%20process.%20Once%20we%20meet%20the%20client%2C%20a%20team%20goes%20to%20their%20location%20and%2C%20in%20a%20matter%20of%2010%20days%2C%20teaches%20them%20to%20make%20%3Cem%3Ekulhads%3C%2Fem%3E%20from%20scratch%20using%20our%20machinery%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20he%20also%20helps%20them%20sell%20their%20%3Cem%3Ekulhads%3C%2Fem%3E.%20%E2%80%9CNow%20that%20I%20have%20been%20in%20the%20business%20for%20some%20time%2C%20and%20also%20due%20to%20the%20popularity%20of%20the%20video%2C%20I%20get%20a%20lot%20of%20calls%20from%20buyers%20from%20different%20parts%20of%20the%20country.%20So%2C%20say%20a%20person%20from%20Karnataka%20wants%20to%20buy%20%3Cem%3Ekulhads%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20I%20will%20locate%20the%20plant%20set%20up%20in%20Karnataka%20and%20connect%20the%20two.%20This%20way%20the%20customer%20gets%20the%20product%20faster%20and%20without%20any%20damages%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShobhit%20has%20set%20up%20over%2045%20%3Cem%3Ekulhad%20%3C%2Fem%3Eplants%20across%20India%20in%20states%20including%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20Maharashtra%2C%20Karnataka%20etc.%20He%20is%20also%20setting%20up%20one%20plant%20in%20Canada%20which%20will%20be%20launched%20in%20January%20next%20year.%20By%20setting%20up%20plants%20in%20different%20states%2C%20he%20has%20formed%20a%20network%20of%20%3Cem%3Ekulhad-%3C%2Fem%3Emakers%20across%20the%20country.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ENot%20his%20first%20attempt%20at%20business%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3ELooking%20back%2C%20Shobhit%20informs%20that%20he%20has%20tried%20his%20hand%20at%20various%20types%20of%20businesses%20before%20finding%20success%20with%20Mittisa.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20was%20in%20college%2C%20I%20started%20a%20course%20where%20I%20taught%20students%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F85389%2Fwhy-effective-communication-can-make-big-difference%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20communication%20skills%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20earned%20a%20turnover%20of%20Rs%2022%20lakhs%20in%20a%20year.%20Then%2C%20I%20started%20an%20AI%20company%20but%20it%20had%20to%20be%20shut%20down%20due%20to%20a%20dispute%20among%20the%20co-founders%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThen%20there%20was%20the%20%3Cem%3Echai%20%3C%2Fem%3Ebusiness%20before%20I%20started%20the%20%3Cem%3Ekulhad%20%3C%2Fem%3Ebusiness.%20You%20never%20know%20what%20would%20hit%20the%20right%20nerve%20in%20the%20market%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESomething%20as%20simple%20as%20%3Cem%3Ekulhad%20%3C%2Fem%3Ehas%20helped%20Shobhit%20to%20earn%20crores%20while%20making%20a%20sustainable%20and%20eco-friendly%20product.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fkulhad-1-1697721886.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22With%20his%20kulhad%20business%2C%20Shobhit%20makes